Server Requirements
===================
* Linux Server, preferably Red Hat based.
* MySQL 5.0 or greater
* Python version 2.5.2 or greater
* Apache httpd 2.0 or greater
* mod_wsgi
* rpmbuild

Application dependencies
========================
* Django 1.2.1
    Download from http://www.djangoproject.com/

* BeautifulSoup Python XML parser.
    Download and install python setuptools.
    Run `easy_install BeautifulSoup`.

Installation from Source
========================
Run the following commands on the linux command prompt and follow instructions.
1. `make rpm HOST=${HOST}`
    where ${HOST} is the hostname of the machine.
2. `rpm -ivh pay4memall-0.1-*.rpm`
3. `pay4memall-setup`
4. Open /etc/httpd/conf.d/pay4memallmod_wsgi.conf in a text editor of your choice and replace the ServerName and ServerAdmin parameters with your server-specific parameters.
5. Restart httpd.
